OL,6,FWhether it's employees or employers,
OL,7,Fthe last two years have been the
OL,8,Ftoughest in living memory, ITV News
OL,9,FInvestigations Editor Dan Hewitt
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FJamie is knackered. The builder sits
OL,13,Fslumped on his sofa, in his one
OL,14,Fbedroom flat in Bridgend, having
OL,15,Ffinished a hard day on the tools.
OL,17,FIt's 7pm. The 35-year-old looks
OL,18,Fmentally as well physically exhausted,
OL,19,Fbut his working day is not yet done.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
