OL,4,Ctaking second jobs
OL,6,FHaving just spent nine hours driving
OL,7,Fforklift trucks and wagons, Jamie will
OL,8,Fsoon leave for his second shift as a
OL,9,Fcleaner at a local office block.
OL,11,F"Bills, food, petrol, clothes, school
OL,12,Ftrips, school uniform - everything has
OL,13,Fjust skyrocketed," the father-of-one
OL,14,Ftells me.
OL,16,F"It just led me to have to permanently
OL,17,Fhave a second job just so the money
OL,18,Fthat I make will cover the bills, and
OL,19,Fthen I've got a bit of cash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
