OL,3,CFocus On: Cost of Living - The workers
OL,4,Ctaking second jobs
OL,6,F"It's just, you can work all the hours
OL,7,Fyou want, but it's just not enough. So
OL,8,Fthe second income was sort of a needs
OL,9,Fmust."
OL,11,FI arrived at Jamie's at the start of
OL,12,Fthe day, just after 5.30am.
OL,14,FHe was up before the sun, and his
OL,15,Fworking day won't end until after it
OL,16,Fhas set.
OL,18,FEvery hour counts, because so does
OL,19,Fevery penny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
