OL,6,FI ask if he has any savings.
OL,8,F"Gone. No savings. Gone in the last
OL,9,Fsix months."
OL,11,FJamie drops Jacob off at his mum's,
OL,12,Fand heads back to the flat. A quick
OL,13,Fbite to eat, and then it's back out to
OL,14,Fwork again.
OL,16,FIt is 9pm, we're still with him. He's
OL,17,Fvacuuming the corridors of an office
OL,18,Fblock a short drive from his house,
OL,19,Fand cleaning the windows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
