OL,6,FI ask Jamie how long he plans to do
OL,7,Fthis for.
OL,9,F"I've burned out before, and you kind
OL,10,Fof do feel just drained, mentally
OL,11,Fexhausted... You need a timeout, but
OL,12,Fbills don't take a timeout.
OL,14,F"It's a week-to-week paycheck. I don't
OL,15,Fknow. I honestly don't know."
OL,17,FFull time workers in Wales are on
OL,18,Faverage #42 per week worse off in real
OL,19,Fterms than they were three years ago,
OL,20,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,21,FStatistics (ONS).
