OL,6,FNearly a third of households (28%)
OL,7,Ftold the Bevan Foundation they've had
OL,8,Fto borrow money to survive in the last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FA few miles away, still in Bridgend,
OL,12,Fin one of South Wales' beautiful
OL,13,Fvalleys, live Rob and Robyn.
OL,15,FThey have three children. The
OL,16,Fyoungest, Imogen, arrived four weeks
OL,17,Fago. She was a wonderful surprise to
OL,18,Ftwo working parents whose other
OL,19,Fchildren are 13 and nine years old.
