OL,6,FThey have been further shocked by the
OL,7,Fcosts that have followed.
OL,9,FWe join Robyn picking up baby supplies
OL,10,Fin her local supermarket.
OL,12,F"Formula, #14.45 - it's quite a lot -
OL,13,FI remember it being #9 when my (elder)
OL,14,Fdaughter was a baby," she says.
OL,16,F"It is quite a worry because
OL,17,Feverything is going up... You know it
OL,18,Fdoesn't cost that much to make, but
OL,19,Fobviously it's profit for the
OL,20,Fcompanies.
