OL,6,F"Nappies, new baby ones, they're #9.
OL,7,FSo she's gone through #36 of nappies
OL,8,Fsince she's been born.
OL,10,F"When she gets into the food stuff, I
OL,11,Fwill make it otherwise you're looking
OL,12,Fat #2 a meal."
OL,14,FBack at their three bedroom home,
OL,15,Fwhich they rent from a housing
OL,16,Fassociation, her husband Rob is
OL,17,Fpreparing to go to work. He's a
OL,18,Fdelivery driver for a supermarket, and
OL,19,Falso plays darts, which sometimes
