OL,6,FThey struggled even before Imogen was
OL,7,Fborn.
OL,9,FRob's wages won't be enough by the
OL,10,Ftime Robyn's maternity pay ends, the
OL,11,Fcouple explains
OL,13,F"Over the years where we have
OL,14,Fstruggled. We've lent money, payday
OL,15,Floans etcetera," says Rob.
OL,17,F"Money comes in, it goes out, and no
OL,18,Fmatter how much money there is, you
OL,19,Falways find something that needs to be
OL,20,Fdone."
