OL,6,F"Basically everything, the monthly
OL,7,Fdirect debits, the bigger bills like
OL,8,Fthe rent, the council tax, the car
OL,9,Finsurance, the car finance... that's
OL,10,Fgone off up," says Robyn.
OL,12,F"It's ridiculous."
OL,14,FThe biggest dilemma ahead for the
OL,15,Fcouple is when, if, Robyn goes back to
OL,16,Fwork as an occupational therapist in
OL,17,Fthe NHS after maternity leave.
