OL,6,FThey need her wage to get by, but the
OL,7,Fcost of nursery fees - which would be
OL,8,Fwell over #1,000 a month if she
OL,9,Freturned full time - has her
OL,10,Fquestioning what's best.
OL,12,F"I have to work... But it's like why
OL,13,Fgo to work when you're paying someone
OL,14,Felse to bring up your children? It
OL,15,Fjust doesn't make sense.
OL,17,F"Yes, you do want to be a good role
OL,18,Fmodel for your children to show them,
OL,19,Flike go out to work every day, but
OL,20,Fthen you're missing out on so much of
OL,21,Ftheir life as well.
