OL,6,FA short drive across to the capital
OL,7,Ffrom Bridgend, we visit Cardiff
OL,8,FGalvanisers, a family-run business
OL,9,Fthat has been brought to its knees by
OL,10,Frising outgoings.
OL,12,FAt a giant metal processing plant,
OL,13,Fwhere they predominantly supply
OL,14,Fproducts for the housing industry, 18
OL,15,Fmonths ago their annual energy bill
OL,16,Fjumped from #280,000 to #1.2 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
